Start when Orion Broker send a notification and the notification is saved in database
n_data = 0
sample = []

While there is a notification of the model in database:
	data = measure from notification
	insert data in sample
	n_data = n_data + 1

	if n_data > window then: 
		save the sample in database		
		n_data = 0
		sample = []

	